# Admin Panel Rules

## Admin Access

- Only users with `admin` role can access admin endpoints
- Use `@Roles('admin')` decorator with `RolesGuard`

## Admin Endpoints

- `GET /api/admin/analytics` - Platform statistics
- `GET /api/admin/requests/pending` - Pending requests for moderation
- `POST /api/admin/requests/:id/approve` - Approve request
- `POST /api/admin/requests/:id/reject` - Reject request
- `GET /api/admin/proposals/pending` - Pending proposals for moderation
- `POST /api/admin/proposals/:id/approve` - Approve proposal
- `POST /api/admin/proposals/:id/reject` - Reject proposal
- `GET /api/admin/users/reported` - Users with reports
- `POST /api/admin/users/:id/block` - Block user
- `POST /api/admin/users/:id/unblock` - Unblock user

## Admin Service

- Get platform analytics and statistics
- Moderate requests and proposals
- Manage user blocking/unblocking
- Review reports
- View platform activity

## Analytics Data

- Total users
- Active requests
- Total proposals
- Revenue (if applicable)
- Growth metrics
- Users by role
- Requests by category
- Activity charts

## Moderation

- Approve/reject requests and proposals
- Provide rejection reason
- Track moderation history
- Notify users about moderation decisions

## User Management

- Block users temporarily or permanently
- Unblock users
- View user reports
- Manage user roles (optional)
